dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.swcomponenttemplate.datatype.datatypes

Interface IRealType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDatatype, IEntity, IIdentifiable, IPrimitiveType, IRange

    public interface IRealType
extends IEntity, IRange
    IRealType: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This represents a range of reals that can be represented by either the IEEE 754 "Single Precision" (encoding is "Single") or IEEE 754 "Double Precision" (encoding is "Double") arithmetic. Note that these standards include representations for +infinity, -infinity, QNaN and SNaN. When defining a RealType, one must indicate whether these special values are allowed or not.
